{"tid":283243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民轟鄭松泰人渣講大話 「熱狗仔隊」獲大筆捐款後無影","createTime":"2017-06-14T04:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T16:50:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc695c470cdc603d85378ff6b0c1d5a93d98eac","tid":283243,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170614/large/1497412952_e113.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170614%2Flarge%2F1497412952_e113.png&h=54bfb8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰的內部會議錄音日前曝光，鄭在錄音中稱要與青年新政梁頌恆、游蕙禎「扮friend」，因「大眾白癡」，以為熱血公民是本土派；又謂去年已與選舉盟友、網台MyRadio創辦人黃毓民「溝通唔到」，稱對方「掂到我底線」。黃毓民前日在網台節目，反斥鄭等人是「人渣」，在錄音中「講大話」，又質疑《熱血時報》早前眾籌設「熱狗仔隊」，獲其老友捐逾20萬，但至今仍未見影。<br />\n<br />\n對於鄭在錄音批評黃毓民創辦的MyRadio，突然暫停由《熱血時報》負責人黃洋達主持的網台節目《大香港早晨》，「掂到」其底線，令他感到不能與黃毓民溝通。黃毓民則反駁鄭，直斥對方「講大話」，「X你老味戾橫折曲，底線，乜X嘢底線啊你嗰條？咩紅線啊？你咁X巴閉？」他又提到自己曾撰長文提及鄭，但因對方「驚X咗黃洋達」，沒有轉發，故致電鄭「XX佢」。<br />\n黃毓民又質疑《熱血時報》早前公開募捐，成立「熱狗仔隊」，但收款後「狗仔隊」卻不見運作，「我啲老友係咁課金畀你，X你老母回水添啊人哋而家追你，狗仔隊喺邊啊？畀X咗廿幾萬你，有晒收條喺度架。」<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民反問黃洋達、鄭松泰等人，「我有咩對你哋唔住啊？除咗我老糊塗信錯你之外，有咩對你唔住啊？」並指自己敗選屬上天眷顧，「呢班真係人渣嚟&hellip;&hellip;選輸呢上天對我就非常之眷顧，（他們）露X晒（真面目）出嚟。」<br />\n對於鄭不滿黃毓民在網台節目中，將組織圍內互相封鎖的內部恩怨，與選舉盟友、城邦論倡議者陳雲所提倡的清算本民前支持者、「清算偽毒派」等具「公共性」的話題扣連，黃毓民亦加以駁斥：「我反對清算，一早話畀你聽架啦，清乜X嘢算啊？清乜X嘢黨啊？大家政見唔同、諗嘅嘢唔同，咪bye bye囉，好X簡單之嘛，啱唔啱啊？我又唔使求你哋。」"},{"pid":"28860dc3e09d3e783456a716e1ac98afc500a1e2","tid":283243,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"第幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58a0d6ee6b4a97851228808e459c397a1181ff3","tid":283243,"uid":57705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c05434243f522f334675766d020b0705061330ae","tid":283243,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第四次"},{"pid":"7aaafb029206d5242425da9652a883b3d2576c67","tid":283243,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"養狼狗咬袋袋"},{"pid":"915271b091c88060cf4512a89204a1d9a0aa0e21","tid":283243,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"有冇屌埋四眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇黎天琦真係最唔反骨嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4733dd7ba44c6d51863442a372f4072cb0b04c0","tid":283243,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"越嚟越覺得熱狗係收錢內哄畀人睇"},{"pid":"5b0d52d7f1942d887f072d1f7de1268775808e6f","tid":283243,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e08f1b232684d36a45623e9832f8aace4593a4f","tid":283243,"uid":10636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"他又提到自己曾撰長文提及鄭，但因對方「驚X咗黃洋達」，沒有轉發，故致電鄭「XX佢」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5246acbeeb5b59ef5370c14dece4a36e421eed34","tid":283243,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"毓民最錯係為咗呢班擦鞋仔同長毛大嚿割席<br />\n割完之後就剩番呢班熱狗人渣攞佢著數分佢光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c96332eb6d4c424f77996ee912f89487ef34682","tid":283243,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有咩對你哋唔住啊？除咗我老糊塗信錯你之外，有咩對你唔住啊？<br />\n<br />\n佢都糊塗左好耐好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩邊都有問題喇，6撚本身有問題，其他人都可能有問題，但6撚今次明顯比熱狗昆鳩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 我都記得熱狗仔隊壇野，當初好似係鳩達講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04ec1464d871b2da0194bee26ab2f8a8925ca2e","tid":283243,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇屌埋四眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇黎天琦真係最唔反骨嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌左啦"},{"pid":"9b5fe2a65cd19f1a2c08dd986f6bcbef785aebab","tid":283243,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de0fc0038b379a71ecb5207648b8c9ef10b8892","tid":283243,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毓民最錯係為咗呢班擦鞋仔同長毛大嚿割席<br />\n割完之後就剩番呢班熱狗人渣攞佢著數分佢光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺得同長毛大舊割蓆有錯"},{"pid":"e48536801792eae9b88f714a0f1cca5a090f30db","tid":283243,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7b1495a7edc54d07d531b771e762d47fb281cf2","tid":283243,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e7e72fb96e5e6f828a2d6c9a9f985ac8b7ecd56","tid":283243,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb56f136cddabd8f86b2c44af9d8cc7d3bac018d","tid":2